24:50.184 --> 24:55.494
♪ BUT ONLY HOW BIG IS HIS HEART

24:55.624 --> 25:00.890
♪ BE THE BEST OF WHATEVER YOU ARE

25:03.676 --> 25:08.507
♪ WHEN EVERY HEART BEATS WIN OR LOSE

25:09.508 --> 25:13.773
♪ DON'T EVER LET LIFE SHOOT YOU DOWN

25:15.731 --> 25:20.562
♪ YOU'RE TALL ENOUGH TO TOUCH THE SKY

25:22.259 --> 25:26.176
♪ BOTH YOUR FEET ARE ON THE GROUND

25:27.961 --> 25:30.877
♪ FIND THE SMILE THROUGH THE TEARS

25:31.007 --> 25:34.054
♪ BURN AWAY YOUR DOUBTS AND FEARS

25:34.184 --> 25:36.883
♪ NO NEED TO WALK ONE STEP BEHIND

25:37.013 --> 25:40.147
♪ IT'S YOUR TURN TO SHINE

25:40.277 --> 25:45.544
♪ BELIEVE IN YOURSELF SAYS♪
♪ THAT ANGEL ON YOUR SHOULDER ♪

25:46.849 --> 25:52.289
♪ IF YOU CAN'T BE THE SUN BE A STAR

25:52.420 --> 25:58.121
♪ BE THE BEST OF WHATEVER YOU ARE

25:58.992 --> 26:04.432
♪ BE THE BEST OF WHATEVER YOU ARE ♪

26:14.181 --> 26:15.138
HI, MATT.

26:15.965 --> 26:17.010
SIMON.

26:17.837 --> 26:18.968
WHERE'D YOU COME FROM?

26:19.752 --> 26:21.144
WHEN YOU'RE MY SIZE, IT'S EASY TO HIDE.

26:21.275 --> 26:23.320
OR SNEAK UP ON PEOPLE.

26:24.583 --> 26:25.714
IF YOU'VE GOT A MINUTE, MATT,

26:25.845 --> 26:27.586
I'D LIKE TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT CARTER.

26:27.716 --> 26:28.891
SURE SIMON.

26:34.505 --> 26:36.072
I ALWAYS WANTED TO LEARN TO SWIM.

26:38.248 --> 26:39.336
IT'S NEVER TOO LATE.

26:41.469 --> 26:44.124
THAT'S WHAT I WAS HOPING
WHEN CARTER CAME TO LIVE WITH ME.

26:47.083 --> 26:48.911
I HEARD YOU AND CARTER TALKING YESTERDAY.

26:50.478 --> 26:51.740
I HEARD WHAT HE SAID ABOUT ME.

26:54.308 --> 26:56.527
MY HOPE WAS THAT HE WOULD NEVER
HAVE TO SUFFER

26:57.093 --> 26:58.704
BECAUSE OF ME BEING A DWARF.

26:59.792 --> 27:02.272
BUT HE IS SUFFERING... AGAIN.

27:04.144 --> 27:06.537
HIS MOTHER THOUGHT
IT'D BE TOO TRAUMATIC FOR HIM

27:06.668 --> 27:08.452
TO KNOW THAT I WAS,

27:08.583 --> 27:12.108
WELL, VERTICALLY CHALLENGED,
AS SHE WOULD PUT IT.

27:14.763 --> 27:17.113
SO WHEN WE DIVORCED,
SHE TOOK OFF WITH CARTER

27:17.244 --> 27:19.986
AND WOULDN'T TELL ME WHERE SHE WAS.

27:21.596 --> 27:26.079
SO CARTER HAD TO SUFFER
BECAUSE HIS FATHER WASN'T AROUND.

27:27.123 --> 27:28.647
AND THINKING THAT I DIDN'T CARE.

27:30.300 --> 27:32.085
I NEVER SHOULD HAVE LET HER
KEEP ME OUT OF HIS LIFE.

27:33.216 --> 27:36.263
I CAN'T REDO THE PAST, BUT I CAN

27:36.393 --> 27:37.960
DO SOMETHING ABOUT THE FUTURE.

27:39.396 --> 27:40.963
CARTER CALLS ME SIMON.

27:42.748 --> 27:45.620
I JUST WANT HIM TO ACCEPT ME
AS HIS FATHER, MATT.

27:47.317 --> 27:51.670
YOU KNOW MY DAD IS TALL,
GOOD LOOKING, CHARMING,

27:52.845 --> 27:56.892
ATHLETIC, WEALTHY, THE WHOLE NINE YARDS,
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

27:58.328 --> 27:59.939
I'M ASHAMED OF MY DAD.

28:03.333 --> 28:06.902
AND IT HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH HIS HEIGHT OR HIS LOOKS.

28:08.077 --> 28:10.079
IT'S 'CAUSE HE WAS A LOUSY DAD...

28:11.211 --> 28:13.692
WHO DIDN'T CARE ABOUT ME OR MY FEELINGS.

28:16.782 --> 28:18.392
AND HE WASN'T THERE FOR ME.

28:18.522 --> 28:20.220
MY DAD WAS SIX FEET TALL.

28:23.614 --> 28:27.183
HE ALWAYS TOLD ME,
"IT DOESN'T MATTER HOW TALL A MAN IS,

28:28.924 --> 28:30.143
AS LONG AS HE HAS HIS FEET ON THE GROUND."

28:33.015 --> 28:34.234
FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH...

28:37.280 --> 28:39.239
I'D BE PROUD TO HAVE YOU AS MY FATHER.

28:42.590 --> 28:44.592
THAT'S WORTH A GREAT DEAL TO ME, MATT.

28:49.162 --> 28:51.077
COME ON. I'LL WALK YOU BACK TO YOUR CAR.

29:11.793 --> 29:12.881
I LOVE THE BEACH.

29:14.535 --> 29:16.667
IT'S SUCH A BEAUTIFUL DAY,
I THINK I'LL DO SOME READING.

29:16.798 --> 29:18.495
HERE?

29:18.626 --> 29:21.063
DON'T WORRY, I'M NOT GONNA HANG
WITH YOU AND YOUR FRIENDS.

29:21.194 --> 29:22.630
I'LL GO FURTHER UP THE BEACH.

29:22.761 --> 29:24.327
OKAY, MY FRIENDS ARE WAITING FOR ME.

29:24.458 --> 29:26.199
I HAVE TO GO.

29:26.329 --> 29:29.332
HEY, WHEN YOU WERE JUST A BABY,
I'D TAKE YOU TO THE BEACH

29:29.463 --> 29:31.030
AND YOU'D NEVER LET GO OF ME.

29:31.160 --> 29:32.379
REMEMBER THAT?

29:33.423 --> 29:35.121
HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO REMEMBER SOMETHING

29:35.251 --> 29:36.818
FROM 10 YEARS AGO WHEN I WAS JUST A BABY?

29:37.340 --> 29:38.777
BESIDES, WHAT'S THERE TO REMEMBER?

29:38.907 --> 29:40.300
WHAT'S THERE TO REMEMBER?

29:41.257 --> 29:43.259
I REMEMBER YOUR FAVORITE FOOD
WAS APPLESAUCE.

29:43.390 --> 29:45.522
I READ DR. SEUSS TO YOU EVERY NIGHT.

29:47.742 --> 29:49.875
AND YOU COULDN'T GO TO SLEEP
UNLESS I ROCKED YOU.

29:50.005 --> 29:52.921
AND YOU HAD THIS LITTLE BEAR
AND YOU CALLED HIM POOKIE.

29:55.445 --> 29:57.578
AND I REMEMBER THE FIRST TIME
YOU LOOKED UP AT ME...

29:58.361 --> 29:59.449
AND CALLED ME DADDY.

30:02.148 --> 30:04.150
I ALSO REMEMBER THE PAIN OF LOSING YOU

30:05.499 --> 30:06.761
WHEN YOUR MOTHER TOOK YOU AWAY.

30:09.416 --> 30:12.332
SO PLEASE, SON, DON'T EVER TELL ME

30:12.462 --> 30:13.507
THERE'S NOTHING TO REMEMBER.

30:17.859 --> 30:19.600
HEY CARTER, WE DON'T HAVE TIME
TO BOOGIE BOARD.

30:19.730 --> 30:20.688
WE GOTTA GET STARTED.

30:21.558 --> 30:23.038
SIMON, I...

30:24.997 --> 30:26.128
CARTER, COME ON!

30:26.825 --> 30:27.913
I GOTTA GO.

30:28.043 --> 30:29.436
HANG ON TO MY BOARD FOR ME?

30:29.566 --> 30:30.611
SURE.

30:33.396 --> 30:36.008
[SOMBER MUSIC]

31:18.659 --> 31:19.703
HOW'S IT GOING?

31:21.096 --> 31:22.054
OKAY.

31:24.056 --> 31:25.057
LOOK...

31:26.885 --> 31:28.321
I OWE YOU AN APOLOGY.

31:28.451 --> 31:30.714
I WAS WRONG TO INTERFERE
WITH YOU AND LOGAN.

31:32.412 --> 31:33.761
I ALSO APOLOGIZED TO LOGAN

31:33.892 --> 31:35.763
AND TOLD HIM HE COULD STAY AT BAYWATCH.

31:37.199 --> 31:38.070
THANKS, STEPH.

31:41.464 --> 31:43.858
SO, I GUESS THAT MUST HAVE BEEN

31:43.989 --> 31:46.208
A PRETTY HARD ONE FOR YOU TO SWALLOW.

31:47.514 --> 31:49.385
A CANTALOUPE WOULD HAVE BEEN EASIER.

31:50.169 --> 31:51.605
HEY, DO YOU REMEMBER THAT POSTER

31:51.735 --> 31:53.259
YOU USED TO HAVE HANGING
OVER YOUR BED AT HOME?

31:55.304 --> 31:57.350
"LOVE MEANS LEARNING TO LET GO."

31:57.480 --> 31:58.873
MM-HMM, YOU JUST USED TO HOPE AND PRAY

31:59.004 --> 32:01.093
THAT SOMEHOW MOM WOULD GET THE DRIFT.

32:01.223 --> 32:04.052
YEAH, SHE NEVER DID, DID SHE?

32:04.183 --> 32:05.097
NO.

32:07.142 --> 32:08.448
WELL, I GET THE DRIFT.

32:09.536 --> 32:11.451
ON-DUTY I'M YOUR BOSS, BUT...

32:14.715 --> 32:17.457
I STILL WANNA BE YOUR SISTER,
YOU KNOW, OFF-DUTY OF COURSE.

32:18.240 --> 32:20.155
BUT, WE ARE NOT GONNA BE
SHARING THE SAME TOWER,

32:20.286 --> 32:22.679
IT'S SORT OF LIKE TEACHING YOU TO DRIVE.

32:22.810 --> 32:24.246
WAIT A SECOND, WHAT IS THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

32:24.377 --> 32:25.813
WHAT WAS SO HARD ABOUT
TEACHING ME HOW TO DRIVE?

32:25.944 --> 32:26.945
ARE YOU KIDDING?

32:27.075 --> 32:28.598
THE WAY YOU SLAMMED ON THE BRAKES

32:28.729 --> 32:31.688
AND GROUND THE GEARSHIFT,
MADE ME A CRAZY PERSON.

32:31.819 --> 32:33.690
WHAT DO YOU MEAN
I MADE YOU A CRAZY PERSON?

32:33.821 --> 32:36.041
YOU MADE ME A CRAZY PERSON.

33:27.353 --> 33:29.877
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

33:44.413 --> 33:47.460
MUFFY, MUFFY, HANG ON I'M COMING!

33:47.590 --> 33:49.114
MUFFY, HANG ON!

34:18.708 --> 34:20.014
HELP!

34:21.275 --> 34:22.277
HELP!

34:23.016 --> 34:24.192
HELP!

34:25.018 --> 34:26.150
HELP!

34:26.934 --> 34:29.980
HELP! HELP! I CAN'T HOLD ON!

34:30.110 --> 34:31.721
HELP!

34:32.853 --> 34:33.940
HELP ME!

34:34.072 --> 34:35.464
HELP!

35:14.460 --> 35:16.244
LET ME GET YOU IN THE BOAT.
COME ON, YOU CAN DO IT.

35:23.817 --> 35:24.861
SIMON.

35:24.992 --> 35:26.515
THERE YOU GO!

35:27.299 --> 35:29.997
THIS IS TOWER 10, I NEED BACKUP
SOUTH SIDE OF THE JETTY.

35:32.826 --> 35:34.523
IT'S SIMON! COME ON! LET'S GO!

35:35.307 --> 35:36.656
COME ON!

36:12.126 --> 36:17.175
[SIREN WAILING]

36:26.488 --> 36:28.621
ASHLEY! ASHLEY, ARE YOU OKAY?

36:30.710 --> 36:31.972
I'M SORRY.

36:32.102 --> 36:33.974
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

37:37.211 --> 37:39.953
MITCH, IT'S SIMON!
HE WENT DOWN ABOUT HERE.

37:51.312 --> 37:52.792
MUFFY, MUFFY...

37:52.922 --> 37:55.273
SIMON! SIMON! WHERE IS HE?

37:55.403 --> 37:57.275
HE'S GOTTA BE OKAY, HOBIE.
HE'S JUST GOTTA.

38:18.252 --> 38:19.906
ALL RIGHT, THEY GOT HIM MAN.

38:25.825 --> 38:27.392
STAND BACK. I GOT HIM, I GOT HIM.

38:27.957 --> 38:30.873
SIMON. SIMON.

38:41.449 --> 38:42.885
JUST KEEP CLEAR, KEEP CLEAR.

