-OKAY, COUGH IT UP.

39:14.177 --> 39:15.918
COME ON, SPIT IT OUT, SPIT IT OUT.

39:16.919 --> 39:19.400
OH DAD, I'M SO SORRY.

39:19.531 --> 39:20.488
YOU OKAY?

39:20.619 --> 39:22.490
DAD, I'M SORRY. DAD, I LOVE YOU.

